<section id="panel" class="section bg-ag-cream">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-ag-ink mb-6">
          Founding Partner Panel
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-ag-muted mb-6">
          Meet the team behind AgD2 Advisors. Our founding partners bring decades of experience in R&D, commercialization, regulatory strategy, and investor readiness.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-ag-muted mb-6">
          Watch our panel discussion to learn how we help AgTech and AgBio startups navigate the critical path from seed funding to venture capital.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border-l-4 border-ag-primary">
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-ag-ink mb-3">Key Topics Covered:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-ag-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ag-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span>What makes AgD2 unique in the advisory landscape</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ag-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Critical gaps startups must address before approaching investors</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ag-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span>How we become an extension of your team</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ag-primary mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span>De-risking strategies for AgTech ventures</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Video -->
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
          <video 
            controls 
            class="w-full aspect-video"
            preload="metadata"
            poster={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}hero-bg.png`}
          >
            <source src="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/fb6385_ef6c165201ce4448bb0f356c23e8c59a/720p/mp4/file.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            <p class="p-4">Your browser doesn't support HTML5 video. <a href="https://video.wixstatic.com/video/fb6385_ef6c165201ce4448bb0f356c23e8c59a/720p/mp4/file.mp4" class="text-ag-primary hover:underline">Download the video</a> instead.</p>
          </video>
        </div>

        <!-- Transcript -->
        <details class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer p-4 font-display font-semibold text-ag-ink hover:bg-ag-cream transition-colors rounded-lg">
            View Full Transcript
          </summary>
          <div class="p-6 text-sm text-ag-muted space-y-4 max-h-96 overflow-y-auto">
            <p>All right. Welcome everyone. Thank you for joining the Founders Leadership Panel for AgD2 Advisors, where deep advisor experience meets your team's needs for your startup company growth...</p>
            <p><em>Note: Full transcript available in the document. Abbreviated here for brevity.</em></p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
